Speed	High	Moderate
________________________________________
6ï¸âƒ£ CRUD Operations in MongoDB
Create
db.users.insertOne({name:"Amit", age:25})

Read
db.users.find({age:25})

Update
db.users.updateOne(
  {name:"Amit"},
  {$set:{age:26}}
)

Delete
db.users.deleteOne({name:"Amit"})

________________________________________
7ï¸âƒ£ Indexing in MongoDB
