2ï¸âƒ£1ï¸âƒ£ Interview / Viva Questions
MongoDB
Q1: Why MongoDB over SQL?
A: Flexible schema, faster, scalable.
Q2: What is BSON?
A: Binary JSON used internally by MongoDB.
________________________________________
API
Q3: What is REST API?
A: Stateless API using HTTP methods.
Q4: Difference between GET and POST?
A: GET fetches, POST creates.
